assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Misumi Co., Ltd. provides energy, lifestyle, and food and beverages related products and services in Japan. Its Energy segment is involved in the wholesale and retail of gasoline, light oil, crude petroleum, lubricants, and other oil related products and LPGs; and provision of delivery services for LPG, as well as construction and inspection services for pressure gas equipment. The company's Lifestyle segment engages in the sale of books, CDs, video games, personal computers, and mobile phones; provision of DVD and CD rental services; sale of houses; sale, maintenance, and inspection of cars; and management of commercial complexes, as well as sale of automobile tires. Its Food & Beverage segment is involved in the management of food chain business; and production and sale of vegetables. The company also manages golf courses; and offers advertising agency services. It sells its products through gas stations, service stations, auto gas service stations, store fronts, and outlets. The company was formerly known as Misumi Petroleum Gas Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Misumi Co., Ltd. in April 1989. Misumi Co., Ltd. was founded in 1959 and is headquartered in Kagoshima, Japan.
